y this cron session is active (no other sessions), send HEARTBEAT_OK only.\\nIf there are no sessions at all, stay SILENT.\\nCurrent time: Tuesday, April 14th, 2026 - 10:16 PM (UTC) / 2026-04-14 22:16 UTC\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"timestamp\": 1776205025798,\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"8c7a2bef\",\n            \"seq\": 1\n          }\n        },\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Let me check the sessions list to find active master-orchestrator sessions.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n              \"id\": \"call_function_hodfom96ej4f_1\",\n              \"name\": \"sessions_list\",\n              \"arguments\": {\n                \"kinds\": [\n                  \"agent\"\n                ],\n                \"activeMinutes\": 120,\n                \"messageLimit\": 2\n              }\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 345,\n            \"output\": 67,\n            \"totalTokens\": 14261,\n            \"cacheRead\": 10789,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 3060,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776205025982,\n          \"responseId\": \"062defe2a31fc7a2d5cc3939359af3c8\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"bb7f52c1\",\n            \"seq\": 2\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:cron:6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"heartbeat\"\n      },\n      \"label\": \"Cron: 5p Progress Report - DTLX\",\n      \"displayName\": \"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-6f3323ef-607e-42a0-b946-611913081d31\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776204838018,\n      \"sessionId\": \"2c4ce7a6-8cd4-4180-beed-b818670b2b3d\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 43953,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776199558073,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/2c4ce7a6-8cd4-4180-beed-b818670b2b3d.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have the heartbeat-state.json and the sessions list. Let me compare them.\\n\\n**Baseline (heartbeat-state.json, lastChecked: 21:37 UTC):**\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ running\\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ running (NEW SESSION — started 21:34 UTC, replaced previous)\\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ✅ done (completed its cycle)\\n- `main` ✅ done (ended ~19:28 UTC)\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ✅ running (stale ~3h+)\\n\\n\\n- **Current sessions (22:13 UTC):** I'm seeing three active cron jobs still running since the baseline, with no new sessions spawned, no failures, and no blockers. The pipeline is healthy, so this appears to be stable.\\n\\nNow I'm cross-referencing the session list more carefully—I notice the cron job IDs have full UUIDs attached to them. The ed2d0b5d session started around 21:29 UTC and has been running for about 23 hours 37 minutes, while the 6f3323ef job started much more recently at 22:05 UTC, running only 1 minute. The third cron (e7885813) appears to be another instance that was replaced by a newer one started at 21:34 UTC.\\n\\nLooking at the heartbeat data, all three cron jobs are showing as running, which aligns with the baseline. The DTLX monitor's 5-minute cycle means it completes frequently, so the state transition from \\\"done\\\" back to \\\"running\\\" is just the normal completion of a cycle. The QLHV group session that ended around 21:49 UTC was just a brief 8-second job that likely just sent a report and shut down—that's not concerning. I'm also noting that a couple of older subagents failed with 500 errors from earlier today, which I should track but aren't critical to the current state.\\n\\nThe pipeline looks solid overall. There are a few failed subagents scattered across different timestamps, but they're all old jobs that aren't blocking anything. No new failures have surfaced in this cycle, so I'm going to keep things quiet and not send out a report.\"\n            },\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"Baseline (21:37 UTC) vs current (22:13 UTC):\\n\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ still running\\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ still running  \\n- `cron:6f3323ef` → cycling back to `running` is **normal cron restart behavior** (5-min cycle), not a state change\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ended ~21:49 UTC (8s runtime, just a report dispatch job — expected)\\n- No failures, no blockers, pipeline HEALTHY\\n\\n**No meaningful state changes. Silent.**\"\n            }\n          ],\n          \"api\": \"anthropic-messages\",\n          \"provider\": \"ahvholding\",\n          \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n          \"usage\": {\n            \"input\": 29592,\n            \"output\": 591,\n            \"totalTokens\": 44544,\n            \"cacheRead\": 13944,\n            \"cacheWrite\": 417,\n            \"cost\": {\n              \"total\": 0\n            }\n          },\n          \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n          \"timestamp\": 1776204870669,\n          \"responseId\": \"062def47dff96fdd6df7c06694b9a908\",\n          \"__openclaw\": {\n            \"id\": \"12d80c37\",\n            \"seq\": 5\n          }\n        }\n      ]\n    },\n    {\n      \"key\": \"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134\",\n      \"kind\": \"other\",\n      \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"origin\": {\n        \"provider\": \"telegram\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"displayName\": \"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"telegram\",\n        \"to\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n        \"accountId\": \"main_bot\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776204726250,\n      \"sessionId\": \"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 51335,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"done\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776162044660,\n      \"endedAt\": 1776162158012,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 113352,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e\",\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"telegram\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"telegram:6053576134\",\n      \"lastAccountId\": \"main_bot\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"🌐 Orbis — Agent Status | 22:06 UTC 14 Apr\\n\\nActive sessions: 2\\n• cron:ed2