 surfaced in this cycle, so I'm going to keep things quiet and not send out a report."},{"type":"text","text":"Baseline (21:37 UTC) vs current (22:13 UTC):\n\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ still running\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ still running  \n- `cron:6f3323ef` → cycling back to `running` is **normal cron restart behavior** (5-min cycle), not a state change\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ended ~21:49 UTC (8s runtime, just a report dispatch job — expected)\n- No failures, no blockers, pipeline HEALTHY\n\n**No meaningful state changes. Silent.**"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":29592,"output":591,"totalTokens":44544,"cacheRead":13944,"cacheWrite":417,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776204870669,"responseId":"062def47dff96fdd6df7c06694b9a908","__openclaw":{"id":"12d80c37","seq":5}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:telegram:direct:6053576134","kind":"other","channel":"telegram","origin":{"provider":"telegram","accountId":"main_bot"},"displayName":"telegram:g-agent-master-orchestrator-telegram-direct-6053576134","deliveryContext":{"channel":"telegram","to":"telegram:6053576134","accountId":"main_bot"},"updatedAt":1776204726250,"sessionId":"8e18daec-1780-455f-b7c4-896849ef86be","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":51335,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776162044660,"endedAt":1776162158012,"runtimeMs":113352,"childSessions":["agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8d8e1952-016d-4c2d-819c-c3b32e3b45b2","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:cd3256cb-3b94-49db-84de-ab99c44cf2fd","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:aa7da6a2-9c14-4261-b1b7-936fb3c60ec8","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:53ffecba-7a14-43e4-91be-9b3efcc56072","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:5d2b77de-dd66-41c2-b053-30aabd324a0e","agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:8bffa95f-1686-4571-a0ed-e69d265eb964"],"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"telegram","lastTo":"telegram:6053576134"