 which is about 28 minutes later. From a state-monitoring perspective, this is normal operation.\n\nThe telegram:group:-5163901258 ending is a clearer state change. Let me verify when it actually ended by converting the timestamp to UTC.\n\nLooking at the duration and start time, the session ran for about 8 seconds and ended around 21:49 UTC on April 14th. But I'm seeing conflicting timestamps in the data—the message at 21:47 says it's still running, while the end timestamp suggests it finished at 21:49. I need to reconcile these different timestamps to understand the actual session lifecycle.\n\nThe baseline at 21:37 showed it as running, so by 22:11 it's clearly ended, which is a change from the previous state. The cron:e7885813 session also appears to have restarted with a new cycle since the last check.\n\nLooking at the session details more carefully, the old session ended around 20:45 UTC and a new one started at 21:34 UTC. By the 22:11 baseline, it had been running for about 37 minutes, and now at 22:11 it's still running after 22 minutes total—so this looks like the same session persisting rather than a restart.\n\nFor cron:6f3323ef, the status shifted from \"done\" in the baseline to \"running\" again, which marks a state change. The DTLX monitor is cycling normally, and the telegram group session has ended. All the sessions are in stable states now with no failures or blockers, so I'll report these as normal cycle completions."},{"type":"text","text":"Baseline is 21:37 UTC. Comparing against current state (22:11 UTC):\n\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d` ✅ still running\n- `cron:e7885813` ✅ still running\n- `cron:6f3323ef` ⚠️ was `done` at 21:37 → now `running` (new cycle)\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258` ⚠️ was `running` → now `ended` (~21:49 UTC)\n- No new failures, no blockers, pipeline healthy\n\n**Two state changes detected. Sending report to group -5163901258 now.**\n\n🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 22:11 UTC 14 Apr\n\nChanges detected:\n• RESTARTED: cron:6f3323ef (DTLX 5p Monitor) — new cycle initiated (was completed at 21:37 UTC)\n• ENDED: telegram:group:-5163901258 — QLHV group session closed ~21:49 UTC (8s runtime)\n\nPipeline: HEALTHY ✅\n• Active sessions: 3 (cron:ed2d0b5d ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ cron:6f3323ef ✅)\n• MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\n• Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\n• Blockers: none\n\n— Orbis 🌐"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"ahvholding","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","usage":{"input":365,"output":1167,"totalTokens":45331,"cacheRead":14272,"cacheWrite":29527,"cost":{"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776204782673,"responseId":"062deeefca2264f272a983ed70e71dd1","__openclaw":{"id":"d995a81a","seq":7}}]},{"key":"agent:master-orchestrator:main","kind":"other","channel":"webchat","origin":{"provider":"heartbeat"},"displayName":"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-main","deliveryContext":{"channel":"webchat","to":"heartbeat"},"updatedAt":1776203469664,"sessionId":"bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45","model":"AHV-Holding-DEV","contextTokens":200000,"totalTokens":91186,"estimatedCostUsd":0,"status":"done","startedAt":1776203458076,"endedAt":1776203464906,"runtimeMs":6830,"systemSent":true,"abortedLastRun":false,"lastChannel":"webchat","lastTo":"heartbeat","transcriptPath":"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl","messages":[{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-14 21:22:23 UTC] Silent. Comparing against stored baseline (20:29 UTC):\nSystem: \nSystem: | Session | Baseline | Current (21:21 UTC) | Δ |\nSystem: |---|---|---|---|\nSystem: | `cron:ed2d0b5d` | ✅ running | ✅ running (~1h51m) | — |\nSystem: | `cron:6f3323ef` | ✅ running | ✅ running | — |\nSystem: | `cron:e7885813` | ✅ running | ✅ running | — |\nSystem: | `main` | ✅ done | ✅ done | — |\nSystem: | `telegram:group:-5163901258` | ✅ running | ✅ running (stale ~33m) | — |\nSystem: \nSystem: All sessions stable. No changes. Pipeline: HEALTHY. Silent.\nSystem: [2026-04